<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Posts on My Blog</title><link>https://zishu-lab.github.io/zishu.github.io/posts/</link><description>Recent content in Posts on My Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.156.0-DEV</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://zishu-lab.github.io/zishu.github.io/posts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>About Markdown Formatting</title><link>https://zishu-lab.github.io/zishu.github.io/posts/about-markdown/</link><pubDate>Tue, 03 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zishu-lab.github.io/zishu.github.io/posts/about-markdown/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="about-markdown-formatting"&gt;About Markdown Formatting&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post demonstrates various Markdown formatting options.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="headings"&gt;Headings&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can use headings to structure your content:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="heading-1"&gt;Heading 1&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id="heading-2"&gt;Heading 2&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="heading-3"&gt;Heading 3&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h2 id="text-formatting"&gt;Text Formatting&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can make text &lt;strong&gt;bold&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;em&gt;italic&lt;/em&gt;, or &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;bold and italic&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can also use &lt;del&gt;strikethrough&lt;/del&gt; text.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="lists"&gt;Lists&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="unordered-lists"&gt;Unordered Lists&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Item one&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Item two
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nested item&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Another nested item&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Item three&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="ordered-lists"&gt;Ordered Lists&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First item&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Second item&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Third item&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id="code"&gt;Code&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can include &lt;code&gt;inline code&lt;/code&gt; in your text.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Sample Post with Images and Tags</title><link>https://zishu-lab.github.io/zishu.github.io/posts/sample-post/</link><pubDate>Tue, 03 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zishu-lab.github.io/zishu.github.io/posts/sample-post/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="sample-post-with-images-and-tags"&gt;Sample Post with Images and Tags&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post demonstrates how to use images and tags in your blog posts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="about-images"&gt;About Images&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When adding images to your blog, you can:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Place them in the &lt;code&gt;static/&lt;/code&gt; directory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reference them using standard Markdown syntax&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;![&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;Alt text&lt;/span&gt;](&lt;span style="color:#50fa7b"&gt;/images/your-image.jpg&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="using-tags"&gt;Using Tags&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tags help organize your content. This post has the following tags:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;sample&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;images&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;blogging&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Readers can click on tags to find related content.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Welcome to My Blog</title><link>https://zishu-lab.github.io/zishu.github.io/posts/first-post/</link><pubDate>Tue, 03 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zishu-lab.github.io/zishu.github.io/posts/first-post/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="welcome-to-my-blog"&gt;Welcome to My Blog!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is my first post on this Hugo blog. I&amp;rsquo;m using the PaperMod theme, which provides a clean and modern design.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="getting-started"&gt;Getting Started&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hugo is a fast and flexible static site generator. With PaperMod theme, you get:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Beautiful minimalist design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Built-in search functionality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsive layout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fast page loads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="whats-next"&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s Next&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ll be adding more content soon. Stay tuned!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>